channel.title: Dafuq
channel.description: Some guy came on my server and started giving himself 99's and spawning items. I'm using project insanity and fake packets are patched. Any ideas?

item.title: Dafuq
item.dc:creator: @looted_y00 looted y00
item.description:
@looted_y00 wrote:

Has he got a username that is built into the commands instead of >=2 its && (username=“blahblah”)
or something like that?
just search for his username in your source and check if it is anywhere besides character files and also check char files for hidden administrator incase one of your friends or coders thought it would be funny to pretend to be someone, and to see if he is one of your admins or owners search his ip to see if it matches another account.
